This turned out really well. I used Lindt bittersweet chocolate and Chamborg instead of eau de vie. This will become a staple at my house.

Rating: 3
I have made this cake three times for small dinnner parties and it always gets raves. Last night I used dried unsweetened Bing cherries, and Chambord for the liqueur, with bittersweet chocolate. I added an extra teaspoon of vanilla. It was the best ever. A great standby when you need an elegant dessert without spending hours on it.

