Rating: 4
This was a simple and tasty recipe. It's not too sweet but very tasty. I wasn't able to find tart cherries so I just used dried bing cherries and it tasted fine. Also, I misread the instructions initially and put parchement paper all the way up the sides of the cake pan. Don't make the same mistake I did! Just cover the bottom with paper.

